{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A unique string identifier for this view that allows you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to reuse this view with multiple similar annotations. You can set this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"parameter to ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if you don’t intend to reuse the view, but it is a good","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"idea in general to specify a reuse identifier to avoid creating redundant","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"reuseIdentifier"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The initialized annotation view object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The reuse identifier provides a way for you to improve performance by recycling","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation views as they enter and leave the map’s viewport. As an annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"leaves the viewport, the map view moves its associated view to a reuse queue.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When a new annotation becomes visible, you can request a view for that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation by passing the appropriate reuse identifier string to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreuseidentifier:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/initWithReuseIdentifier:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)initWithReuseIdentifier:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L77"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/initWithReuseIdentifier:":{"title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreuseidentifier:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/initWithReuseIdentifier:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"type":"topic","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection"}}}